name.k: Sky Whale - a Game Shakers App

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: In Nickelodeon’s TV series Game Shakers, Sky Whale plays the part of a hit game created by two 13-year-old girls who headline the show. You don’t have to be a Game Shakers fan to enjoy the charmingly fun Sky Whale, which Nickelodeon released as a tie-in game. As you send a cute purple narwhal spiraling through the air by feeding it donuts or bouncing it off toilets, the game’s slapstick, kid-friendly energy is irresistible. We were quickly engrossed by the challenge of keeping that whale airborne as long as possible—and laughed more than a few times along the way.
